SUMMARY:Build\, Scale & Govern AI Agents
DESCRIPTION:Microsoft Reactor Toronto\nIn this session\, you’ll explore how to design scalable and reliable multi‑step AI agents by combining agentic RAG techniques\, MCP‑based tool use\, and proven agent design patterns. We’ll break down how these components work together to create agents that reason effectively\, coordinate tasks\, and integrate seamlessly with external systems.\n\nThrough practical examples and reusable patterns\, you’ll learn how to build agents that can scale across teams\, extend to complex workflows\, or be adapted for your personal projects. You’ll leave with a toolkit of approaches you can immediately apply to accelerate your agent development journey.\n\n-----------------------------------------------\n[The Java Script AI Build-a-thon](https://aka.ms/JSAIBuildathon)\n\n📌 This session is a part of a series! Learn more [here](https://developer.microsoft.com/reactor/series/S-1628/?wt.mc_id=meetup_S-1628_webpage_reactor)
